04:03.757 --> 04:05.457
Yes. Imagine some day you live

04:05.525 --> 04:07.092
in a four-story walk-up apartment.

04:07.160 --> 04:08.293
What, like a brownstone?

04:08.361 --> 04:10.396
Yes, like a brownstone.

04:10.463 --> 04:13.399
Now, you've got to get a heavy
crate of oranges upstairs.

04:13.466 --> 04:15.200
