you're talking about.

07:09.309 --> 07:10.542
I had a bully once.

07:10.610 --> 07:12.544
Stelio Kontos was his name.

07:12.612 --> 07:15.314
He was as mean as he was Greek.

07:15.381 --> 07:18.784
<i>He made my life a
living hell.</i>

07:18.852 --> 07:20.986
<i>He totally tormented me.</i>

07:21.054 --> 07:22.688
<i>One time he made me</i>

07:22.756 --> 07:24.923
<i>keep a live bat</i> <i>in my underpants
all day.</i>

07:24.991 --> 07:26.692
<i>Gave me ass rabies.</i>

07:26.760 --> 07:28.727
<i>My anus was frothing</i> <i>like a cappuccino.</i>

07:30.563 --> 07:33.132
