07:34.868 --> 07:36.568
The kind that bullies his own son?

07:36.636 --> 07:38.904
Right. You see, Steve,
the good thing about bullies is

07:38.972 --> 07:40.239
they don't just go away.

07:40.306 --> 07:41.740
You're forced to deal with them.

07:41.808 --> 07:43.108
How did you deal with Stelio?

07:43.176 --> 07:44.343
Mm, good story.

07:44.410 --> 07:45.544
He moved away.

07:46.846 --> 07:48.280
But your bully's
not going anywhere.

07:48.348 --> 07:49.448
So deal with him.

07:49.516 --> 07:51.383
You'll be better off for it.

07:53.486 --> 07:54.553
Steve!

07:54.621 --> 07:55.888
Oh, my God!

07:55.955 --> 07:58.624
Who did this to you?!

07:58.691 --> 08:01.360
You better not say a word,
or I'll kill you!

08:02.362 --> 08:03.695
It was not Dad.

08:03.763 --> 08:05.397
Okay, it wasn't Dad.

08:05.465 --> 08:07.466
Good. We're narrowing it down.

08:07.534 --> 08:09.668
