08:29.355 --> 08:31.089
I... I-I don't know.

08:31.157 --> 08:32.957
Stand up for yourself. Fight me!

08:34.360 --> 08:36.628
Well, I'm gonna mount
this and ride it hard...

08:36.696 --> 08:39.097
