09:43.096 --> 09:45.564
Hey, you guys want to see
where all the clowns sleep?

09:45.632 --> 09:46.832
It's super sad.

09:46.900 --> 09:48.133
Yeah, sure.

09:48.201 --> 09:51.136
Oh, but we were about to
go on the Ferris Wheel.

09:51.204 --> 09:53.472
Oh, that's okay. You two go ahead.

09:53.539 --> 09:54.973
I'm gonna eat a whole turkey leg,

09:55.041 --> 09:56.909
